由中環行去維園<br />\n啫係中環（近金鐘同西環）會儲好撚多人<br />\n而且交通會集中晒，驚甴係佈防上用唔返一直用開嗰個<br />\n而遊行期間行到金鐘就失控點算，佢冇得跟上次噉，由中環去金鐘只係有好少空間俾佢佈陣cut人龍清人數，因為佢cut完之後啲人就係喺晒中環，交通又斷咗，如果幾十萬人唔走，佢一世都清唔到。仲未計留返幾十萬「暴徙」喺中環，佢點擔當得起？"},{"pid":"bcb2d55ccf1218f910c40b8022fd50781fb8b010","tid":1826990,"uid":11013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思 謝一謝位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n和理非 手足 家長 學生都請入黎 <br />\n<br />\ntg 支足channel<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/materials201920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmaterials201920&d=LzGu2J%2BtBqWvyoHzd7Q7GNMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=9056ac8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/materials201920</a>"},{"pid":"9eb2e30ac742ce4b11f8d4a9a8efc3be25629668","tid":1826990,"uid":55956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T00:53:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c527604dfcbfa8ad212f8dfd4879b0a5805f0c5c","tid":1826990,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T04:55:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"3f481aed44b1ee86ab4a3be374d31a649a536142","tid":1826990,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T06:28:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2798a35656a8235be8af2c7bdf9251b80162b4aa","tid":1826990,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:43:47.000Z","msg":"戈"},{"pid":"b885e9f5eeabff370ce8a45209beb2c3044c1405","tid":1826990,"uid":105114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-17T09:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1225e41103fa082dc0b2e49ad73cafd47bd0fff","tid":1826990,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-